&lt;ul data-list-tree=&quot;true&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As an engineer, your focus will be on developing and maintain, modular and reusable systems, explore new technologies and find solutions to enhance our products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll participate on design discussions, troubleshoot complex problems, and contribute directly to our codebase.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll also play a key part in building a collaborative, high-performing team culture. Whether reviewing code, or supporting other engineers and tech lead..&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
